================================================================================
Scope — what this license does and does not cover
================================================================================

The MIT license above covers the SOFTWARE in this repository: the site
(index.html, plant.html, styles.css, reel.js, app.js, plant.js) and the Python
tools in tools/.

It does NOT cover the plant PHOTOGRAPHS. Each photo is the work of its
individual photographer and is used under that photographer's own
open license — CC0, CC-BY, CC-BY-SA, or CC-BY-NC (or public domain). The
photographer and license for every photo are recorded in the plant's data
(`plants/<category>/<slug>/plant.json` and `images/credits.json`). Because
several photos are CC-BY-NC, the photo collection as a whole is for
non-commercial use; reuse any individual photo only under its own terms, and
always keep the attribution.

The written plant descriptions and growing/care notes (the prose in the
`plant.json` files) are released under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0
International (CC-BY-4.0): https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
